At the very outset, I would like to tell you

00:10:39.874 --> 00:10:47.041
that the truth is you are not this body, this mind,

00:10:47.248 --> 00:10:56.342
these emotions, intellect, conditionings, or your ego.

00:10:58.689 --> 00:11:03.185
But you are the pure Spirit.

00:11:04.275 --> 00:11:09.940
There is another truth is, you see all these beautiful flowers

00:11:10.140 --> 00:11:13.765
and we take them for granted.

00:11:14.107 --> 00:11:17.771
Actually, it's a miracle.

00:11:19.355 --> 00:11:22.952
If you ask a doctor who runs your heart,

00:11:23.152 --> 00:11:27.448
so he will say, It is the autonomous nervous system.

00:11:28.219 --> 00:11:32.366
But who is this auto?

00:11:32.567 --> 00:11:35.497
Also, if you take to science

00:11:35.698 --> 00:11:37.756
you will find they cannot answer

00:11:37.957 --> 00:11:42.866
all the questions because it has its own limitations.

00:11:44.854 --> 00:11:50.338
